descript.abstract: The data set depicts the coastal zone management boundaries of most coastal states of the conterminous U.S. This data set was obtained from NOAA's Special Projects Office coastal demographics Web site (http://marineeconomics.noaa.gov/socioeconomics/welcome.html) and modified by NOAA's Coastal Services Center (CSC) to include the coastal zone of Wisconsin.
descript.purpose: This data set is intended for use in comparison to other jurisdictional boundaries.
